<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sorrow-n">sorrow <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sɒrəʊ/    美 /'sɑːroʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>悲伤；悲痛：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They learnt <strong>great sorrow</strong> and happiness, and finally they learnt wisdom.
他们历经大悲大喜，最终获得智慧。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 2改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To his <strong>deep sorrow</strong>, his grandfather died in a car accident yesterday.
令他悲痛万分的是，他的爷爷昨天丧生于车祸。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>伤心事；不幸事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>joys and sorrows of life
人生的悲欢</p></div></div>